key: You can change the order by dragging the banner.
en: You can change the order by dragging the banner.
lo: ທ່ານສາມາດ ຈັດລຽງ ໂດຍການລາກໃຫ້ລຽງຕາມລຳດັບທີ່ຕ້ອງການ.

key: You can change the status after filling in.
en: You can change the status after filling in.
lo: ທ່ານສາມາດເລືອກສະຖານະຫລັງຈາກໃສ່ຂໍ້ມູນແລ້ວ

key: You can change the status after registering all the items.
en: You can change the status after registering all the items.
lo: ທ່ານສາມາດປ່ຽນສະຖານະ ຫລັງຈາກໄດ້ບັນທຶກທຸກລາຍການ

key: You can change the status after the car doctor checks all 275 items.
en: You can change the status after the car doctor checks all 275 items.
lo: ທ່່ານສາມາດປ່ຽນສະຖານະ ຫລັງຈາກຜູ້ກວດສອບລົດ ສໍາເລັດການກວດສອບທັງຫມົດ 275 ລາຍການ

key: You can only enter english, number and special characters.
en: You can only enter english, number and special characters.
lo: ທ່່ານສາມາດໃສ່ໄດ້ພາສາອັງກິດ ຕົວເລກ ແລະ ຕົວອັກສອນພິເສດ ເທົ່ານັ້ນ

key: You can pin up to 5 posts.
en: You can pin up to 5 posts.
lo: ປັກໝຸດສູງສຸດໄດ້ 5 ອັນ.

key: You can upload up to 4 photos.
en: You can upload up to 4 photos.
lo: ທ່ານສາມາດອັບໂຫຼດຮູບ ສູງສຸດ 4ຮູບ

key: You can upload up to 10 photos.
en: You can upload up to 10 photos.
lo: ທ່ານສາມາດອັບໂຫຼດຮູບ ສູງສຸດ 10ຮູບ

key: You can upload up to 20 photos.
en: You can upload up to 20 photos.
lo: ທ່ານສາມາດອັບໂຫຼດຮູບ ສູງສຸດ 20ຮູບ

key: You cannot modify the details once the productization process is completed, please modify in this process if any revisions are needed.
en: You cannot modify the details once the productization process is completed, please modify in this process if any revisions are needed.
lo: ທ່ານບໍ່ສາມາດແກ້ໄຂລາຍລະອຽດຫລັງຈາກຂັ້ນຕອນການຜະລິດສໍາເລັດ, ກະລຸນາແກ້ໄຂຂັ້ນຕອນນີ້ ຫາກມີມີຄວາມຈໍາເປັນຕ້ອງແກ້ໄຂ

key: You cannot request for more verification code. Please try again later.
en: You cannot request for more verification code. Please try again later.
lo: ບັນຊີໄດ້ຖືກລັອກເນື່ອງຈາກມີຄໍາຮ້ອງຂໍລະຫັດຢືນຢັນຫຼາຍຄັ້ງ. ກະລຸນາລອງໃໝ່ໃນພາຍຫຼັງ.

key: You’re using a web browser we don’t support. Please use one of these options to improve your experience.
en: You’re using a web browser we don’t support. Please use one of these options to improve your experience.
lo: ທ່ານກໍາລັງໃຊ້ເວັບບຣາວເຊີທີ່ພວກເຮົາບໍ່ຮອງຮັບ. ກະລຸນາໃຊ້ຫນຶ່ງໃນທາງເລືອກເຫຼົ່ານີ້ເພື່ອປັບປຸງປະສົບການຂອງທ່ານ.

key: Your message has been sent successfully.
en: Your message has been sent successfully.
lo: ຂໍ້ຄວາມຂອງທ່ານໄດ້ຖືກສົ່ງໄປແລ້ວ.
